Index entries for sequences that are permutations of the natural numbers
mathematica: (* b = A262356 *) b[1] = 1; b[n_] := b[n] = Module[{s, k}, s = Rest[ IntegerDigits[b[n-1]]] //. {(0).., d__} :> {d}; For[k = 2, True, k++, If[FreeQ[Array[b, n-1], k], If[s == {0}, Return[k], If[IntegerDigits[ k][[1 ;; Length[s]]] == s, Return[k]]]]]];
Sort[Table[{b[n], n}, {n, 1, 2 terms}]][[1 ;; terms, 2]] (* _Jean-François Alcover_, Mar 12 2019 *)
